properties.name: Museum of Jurassic Technology
properties.description: Posted by Jason 9341 Venice Blvd, Culver City, CA"...guided along as it were a chain of flowers into the mysteries of life." Like a coat of two colors, the Museum serves dual functions. On the one hand the Museum provides the academic community with a specialized repository of relics and artifacts from the Lower Jurassic, with an emphasis on those that demonstrate unusual or curious technological qualities. On the other hand the Museum serves the general public by providing the visitor a hands-on experience of "life in the Jurassic"....
